			<referenceToDataSource type="source data set" refObjectId="e5c72486-7eeb-4a62-ab63-c8e4a0880569" uri="../sources/e5c72486-7eeb-4a62-ab63-c8e4a0880569.xml">
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="en">Xu, L., Zhang, S., Yang, M., Li, W. &amp; Xu, J. Environmental effects of China’s solar photovoltaic industry during 2011–2016: A life cycle assessment approach. Journal of Cleaner Production 170, 310–329 (2018).</common:shortDescription>
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="zh">Xu, L., Zhang, S., Yang, M., Li, W. &amp; Xu, J. Environmental effects of China’s solar photovoltaic industry during 2011–2016: A life cycle assessment approach. Journal of Cleaner Production 170, 310–329 (2018).</common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToDataSource>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When applying the data set derived from the life cycle inventory (LCI) of China's solar PV industry for the period 2011-2016 for environmental impact assessments, users should ensure consistent methodology with previously established literature, particularly that referenced in the description (e.g., Fu et al., 2015; He, 2013; Hong et al., 2016, etc.). Consideration of the specific multiple-row delay blasting technique in silicon ore extraction must be included when modelling the environmental impacts of silicon production for solar PV systems. Additionally, accurate representation of the solar PV system configuration, efficiency, and the time period of study is crucial for accurate results.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在应用2011-2016年中国太阳能光伏产业生命周期清单（LCI）数据集进行环境影响评估时，用户应确保与先前建立的文献中的方法论一致，特别是描述中引用的文献（例如，傅等人，2015; 何，2013; 洪等人，2016等）。在模拟太阳能光伏系统硅生产的环境影响时，必须包括硅矿多排延时爆破技术的具体考虑。此外，准确表征太阳能光伏系统的配置、效率和研究时期对于获得准确结果至关重要。</useAdviceForDataSet>
		</dataSourcesTreatmentAndRepresentativeness>
